Create Rolling Weeks Inverse Column and Play Axis on Scatter Plot 28

Step 1: Create Rolling Weeks Inverse Column and Play Axis on Scatter Plot

- Select Modeling and then select new column. Paste this in the value box (Rolling Weeks Inverse = HW_Grading[RollingWks] * -1)

- Select the scatter plot chart and then in the fields place the new Rolling weeks Inverse column in the play axis.
